title: 27 - Lev Fer

description: Leviathan Ferrywings! Or that’s how Lev Fer is saved in Sean’s phone. He’s a very funny stand-up making his way up the ranks at the top clubs in the city. He’s got his own podcast Yung Daddy, was named one of New York Comedy Festivals 2019 Comics to Watch, and he’s got a killer story for you. Here are five words to describe this episode: don’t gamble away your money.
